1. *Slušaj* me pažljivo! (Listen to me carefully!)
2. Njegova rečenica je bila: *Slušaj* šta ti govorim. (His sentence was: Listen to what I'm telling you.)
3. *Slušala* sam ga satima. (I listened to him for hours.)
4. Ona je stalno *slušala* moje savete. (She was constantly listening to my advice.)
5. *Slušamo* muziku. (We are listening to music.)